asset.title: Penny Skateboards X The Hundreds
asset.description:
To see the board yourself- visit http://www.pennyskateboards.com !

Following the success of the first collaboration board, Penny and The Hundreds have teamed up yet again to introduce the The Hundreds X Penny" Nickel" Skateboard. The deck features an overlay of The Hundreds' custom Duck Camo print, as well as The Hundreds' commemorative ten-year Bar logo emblazoned across the board in orange type. Additional highlights include custom 4" black Penny trucks, orange 59mm 78A Penny wheels, Penny Abec7 bearings, and assorted Penny Skateboards branding throughout.
